@baseUrl = https://localhost:7288

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List All Registered Agents
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agents

### List All Workflow Definitions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows

### Execute Sales Stalled Deal Recovery Workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workflows/sales-stalled-deal-recovery/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "dealId": "OPP-48291",
    "daysStalled": 11,
    "amount": 480000,
    "ContactEmail": "buyer@enterprise.com"
}

### Publish a Stalled Deal Event (triggers workflow via event bus)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "source": "Salesforce",
    "eventType": "sales.opportunity.stalled",
    "department": "Sales",
    "severity": 2,
    "payload": {
        "dealId": "OPP-99182",
        "daysStalled": 14,
        "amount": 320000
    }
}

### Evaluate a Governance Policy
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/governance/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "agentId": "sales-pricing",
    "workflowInstanceId": "test-001",
    "stepId": "step-1",
    "action": "Execute money transfer",
    "department": "Sales"
}

### Get Audit Trail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit

### Get Audit Trail for Specific Agent
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit?agentId=sales-deal-analysis

### Get Impact Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/impact

### Get Impact Dashboard (board-level metrics)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/impact/dashboard

### Get Sales Department Impact
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/impact?department=Sales